dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Columbia County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Columbia County, Wisconsin in 2014. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Columbia_Hydro_2014.gdb. The layers included in this geodatabase are 'Columbia_HydroLine_2014' and Columbia_HydroPoly_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For most current data, please visit http://www.co.columbia.wi.us/ColumbiaCounty/landinformation/InteractiveMapping/tabid/235/Default.aspx
